April Rain Song

Let the rain kiss you.
Let the rain beat upon your head
With silver liquid drops.
Let the rain sing you
A lullaby.

The rain will make the flowers grow.
The rain will send me
A message
To put in my heart:
Let the rain kiss you.

- Langston Hughes
